<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٩٦٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4563">عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: كَتَبْتُ عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7230">يُوسُفَ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٧٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بْنِ الْمَاجِشُونِ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2829">صَالِحِ بْنِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/65">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3378">جَدِّهِ </a>: فِي بَدْرٍ يَعْنِي حَدِيثَ ابْنَيْ عَفْرَاءَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>